    "en": {
      "title": "An unknown corpse stops three trains",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "166 km between Kital Ella and Heiloya railway stations on Udara railway line, 3 trains have stopped midway due to a dead body on the railway track.",
        "The Udarata Menike train that left Badulla for Colombo Fort today morning at 5/55 has been stopped at Ella station and two mail trains which were running from Colombo to Badulla have been stopped at Bandarawela and Haputale.",
        "Bandarawela police said that they will have to wait for the arrival of a coroner to remove the body."
      ],
